data.description: Beautiful Custom Log Home built by The Pelc Brothers  Drive back the lane of your private 10+ acres  offering pastures, tillable acreage, pond, golf course frontage, and a spectacular view!  Home offers 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, vaulted ceilings, spiral staircase, double sided fireplace, victorian gas stove, custom cherry kitchen with Italian tile,  owners suite with double closets, and whirlpool tub.  Home is freshly sanded and stained, newer metal roof, superior walls,  Anderson windows, 200 amp service panel, and new water heater & well pump.   This rare find is located next to golfing,  just minutes away from Michaux State Forest and the Lakes, a short drive  to Rt. 30 and Rt. 15,  and near the historic downtown Gettysburg!   Property is enrolled in the clean and green program for added tax relief
